      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Job 38:7",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). Note also the distinction between the \"light\" and the \"lamp.\" The righteous ones have the true light in them. That which belongs to the wicked is only derived and temporary, and even that shall be extinguished before long. Compare a like distinction in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "John 1:8",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
